pid":"7e3ba8dfba5d7a99e3d19d3a1ccb4507607d1c92","tid":664403,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f11fab55196f2338f46900393bae5afa6f391b","tid":664403,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:29:14.000Z","msg":"要比地税咪即係唔係九九九年期囉，有九九九年期既係地稅、地租乜都唔使比，你識唔識呀"},{"pid":"4e20f726e086dafc7b2b89061841779976b1fd21","tid":664403,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cf8cfe6415fa0bfdd8c7db27ee68fdacec06363","tid":664403,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:27:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:33:08.000Z","msg":"港島區有啲係一九八五年以後批出，冇九九九年期既地，嗰啲樓係要交地稅（唔係地租），我而家係針對九九九年期嗰啲乜鳩都唔使比既豪宅，係你唔識分定我唔識分？"},{"pid":"f01ed734204ab7b5328b2befcd74ab269e3a0623","tid":664403,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3edd93394212411cc454fc2d4c2a979fba12cc8a","tid":664403,"uid":150117,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"b2b6053d27ab5e0858cb110628690da6339fac97","tid":664403,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"af466a83dacceffd784ed78a6fcd023a3441be2d","tid":664403,"uid":150117,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:41:09.000Z","msg":"就算係999年地契樓未必係豪宅，可以係普通住宅。你有冇唸過住港島都可以係普通小市民黎？港島某D樓貌似唔洗交地租好似好爽咁，但其實我地交既差餉一定高過新界同類型住宅，拉勻返。<br />\n<br />\n新界差餉+地租=港島差餉<br />\n<br />\n係呢度要載返頭盔，2018至2019年度，我地連一蚊物業稅都唔洗交比政苦✌🏻✌🏻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:56:26.000Z","msg":"咁點同，差餉係根據應課差餉租值嚟計，你個單位值錢啲，比多啲差餉，將來賣出去貴啲，咁係應該既。<br />\n<br />\n如果我地比差餉加地租=等於你地差餉，但我地樓價同租值比你地低，咁叫做唔公平囉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:04:14.000Z","msg":"甘係港島買樓個陣，我地都比左一個較高樓價個wor,又公唔公平呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z4wqgu3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZ4wqgu3.gif&h=2c1ad03a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41504a6fae58170bc0db2506c6b95c196604f67b","tid":664403,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:42:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9093cca1805655d855f1091a0cc18b6d3c830a5e","tid":664403,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:42:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"128a0196696cbeeabb36a1bc74ff948919d2ffac","tid":664403,"uid":124623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"界限街以南係叫地稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （中英聯合聲明之後批出既地另計）<br />\n地稅同地租都係計你3%，不過前者fix死咗你續期果日黎計，後者係浮動，只要樓市一日唔跌，一定係前者抵玩，唔知有冇人明呢個point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過呢，界限街以南d樓係貴到飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到樓上有人話自己港島屋苑冇收過地稅，得兩種可能，一係棟樓塊地係中英聯合聲明之後先批出，就會收地租；一係你棟樓塊地未夠期，仲係成個地段咁收地稅，會係好平地稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓上仲有人提999年期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即是未夠期續（你可以理解做永遠唔會續期啦）所以仲係整個地段咁收地稅法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前香港開埠初期d地都係批999年（即是港島最值錢d地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）同埋果時港英政府唔知有冇官商勾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下太x集團d樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知解唔解答到樓豬問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後都係果句，港島d樓貴到飛起啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ddfb629ea1372fc6df98ad9b5e7637934d205d","tid":664403,"uid":124623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e3ba8dfba5d7a99e3d19d3a1ccb4507607d1c92","tid":664403,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f1